</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1437,151,753]" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">
<materialsCitation ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3014903335" collectionCode="MNHP" country="Venezuela" county="Piauhy" location="Nevertheless" municipality="Vera Cruz" pageId="3" pageNumber="234" specimenCount="2" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" typeStatus="holotype">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,363,402,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">
<typeStatus box="[199,258,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Type</typeStatus>
locality:
</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Friese, H." box="[371,523,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="234" pagination="39 - 48" refId="ref21677" refString="Friese, H. (1899) Neue arten der Bienengattungen Epicharis Klug und Centris Fabr. Termeszetrajzi Fuzetek, 23, 39 - 48." type="journal article" year="1899">Friese (1899)</bibRefCitation>
mentioned that the specimens he studied were from 
<collectingCountry box="[1126,1244,403,429]" name="Venezuela" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Venezuela</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[1256,1324,403,429]" name="Brazil" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingCounty box="[1341,1421,403,429]" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Piauhy</collectingCounty>
= Piauí) and 
<collectingCountry box="[271,357,439,465]" name="Mexico" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Mexico</collectingCountry>
(
<collectingMunicipality box="[370,485,439,465]" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Vera Cruz</collectingMunicipality>
= 
<collectingRegion box="[506,611,439,465]" country="Mexico" name="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Veracruz</collectingRegion>
). 
<location LSID="urn:lsid:plazi:treatment:8422F619C512BD52FF15F89F5081FD44:095411D4C513BD52FDF6FE1B5260FE64" box="[628,776,439,465]" country="Venezuela" county="Piauhy" municipality="Vera Cruz" name="Nevertheless" pageId="3" pageNumber="234" stateProvince="Veracruz de Ignacio de la Llave">Nevertheless</location>
, the specimen found at 
<collectionCode box="[1036,1116,439,465]" country="USA" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/3kvn-7rck" name="Princeton University" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">MNHP</collectionCode>
bears a label “Hte Vera Paz” (= Haute Vera Paz). This locality is actually in 
<collectingCountry box="[677,801,475,501]" name="Guatemala" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
, not in 
<collectingCountry box="[884,972,475,501]" name="Mexico" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">Mexico</collectingCountry>
, so the 
<typeStatus box="[1057,1105,475,501]" pageId="3" pageNumber="234">type</typeStatus>
locality is different from that cited by him
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
